{"tid":1987632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】李元玲騷每日一貼呼籲留家抗疫　網友：妳給大家力量","createTime":"2020-04-24T15:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T15:14:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0abb4eb41cb64f9653e291d060e838bb744975d","tid":1987632,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情下，不少國家都呼籲市民留在家中，甚至規定非必要是不準外出。有「大馬鋼琴女神」之稱的李元玲，除了用靚相為粉絲解悶外，也會有一些小互動。例如今日（24/04）她也在IG上說笑道：「我們的『假期』是不是又被充值了兩禮拜？#Stayhome」網民則留言說：「對呀，你也填坑了？」也有人說：「妳給大家力量」，更有人玩開笑道：「自動儲值！」無論要留家抗疫多久，有李元玲陪住大家過，都算是一個安慰。"},{"pid":"34f633bcba4f12e7bcf9d6e30130c63e0acd8d5a","tid":1987632,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4379786/org/913845601c9a4b4b321c46ca6aec89e6.jpg/ip5IEFLFhw2h3fcePQmXbeuj3IGvh4ijdQOVcXUDlXE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4379786%2Forg%2F913845601c9a4b4b321c46ca6aec89e6.jpg%2Fip5IEFLFhw2h3fcePQmXbeuj3IGvh4ijdQOVcXUDlXE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e938cc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李元玲幾乎每日都會貼靚相。（IG@cathrynli）"},{"pid":"81e416ea9e36d2c7e5bb6a8addfcbde57bc98b67","tid":1987632,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4333764/org/37f69a0a0ca11478c57333d96a65b731.jpg/3FZYtyct39ZKSWyyzk9P5yGeCOKgJVkZZO-rf2Tvq38\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4333764%2Forg%2F37f69a0a0ca11478c57333d96a65b731.jpg%2F3FZYtyct39ZKSWyyzk9P5yGeCOKgJVkZZO-rf2Tvq38&h=03256731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4320712/org/0bfa862b0923d5db1cb43c8703632231.jpg/6G--9iQxpq3ttRdkDUG6e1ghcWXMAm2tmmfF7Zpnxe0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4320712%2Forg%2F0bfa862b0923d5db1cb43c87036322